# Copy this file to ".env.local" for local development, and set the same
# variable in your host's dashboard (Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables)
# for production.
#
# Your Firebase Realtime Database URL. Find it in the Firebase console:
#   Build → Realtime Database → the URL shown at the top of the Data tab.
# It looks like one of these (region varies):
#   https://YOUR-PROJECT-default-rtdb.firebaseio.com
#   https://YOUR-PROJECT-default-rtdb.europe-west1.firebasedatabase.app
#
# When this is set, game rooms sync across real phones. When it's empty, the
# app falls back to same-browser-only sync (fine for local testing).
VITE_FIREBASE_DB_URL=
